\emph default

\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

 The conditional distribution 
\begin_inset Formula $G_{Y}(y\mid t)$
\end_inset

 does not depend on 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 and is identical to the distribution of 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

, i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $Exp(\lambda)$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset VSpace 1cm
\end_inset

 
